The l Isa location
End The l.

The o Isa object
End The o.

The a Isa actor
End The a.

Start At l.
  Use Script x For o. -- Error, not an actor
  Use Script x For a. -- Error, does not have the script
  If o Isa actor Then
    Use Script x For o. -- Error, not an actor since instance id's are not considered for restriction
    Use Script x For a. -- Error, does not have the script
  End If.

